~Could you add an additional check for x64 host arm64 crossbuild, since it's currently blocked by https://github.com/flutter/flutter/issues/74929. Something like:~

```
// TODO(fujino): https://github.com/flutter/flutter/issues/74929
if (_operatingSystemUtils.hostPlatform == HostPlatform.linux_x64 && targetPlatform == TargetPlatform.linux_arm64) {
  throwToolExit('Cross-build from Linux x64 host to Linux arm64 target is not currently supported.');
}
```

